so this is kind of a post way overdue…. but I felt like it was on my heart today to share about God and how great he is. Even through the hard days, God is great 🤍 and I just wanted to give praise to God for all the amazing things he’s done in my life 🙏🏽 ever since I was a little girl he has had plans for me and has followed me through every single journey, through the obstacles, and the highs and low. His love is unconditional and so strong and I just felt like I needed to post this. Whether you are doing great in life or you have been feeling low, talk to God because he is ALWAYS there and listening and wants a relationship with YOU and your heart 🤍He knows what’s meant to happen in your life and he has a plan for each and every one of us. God will never give up on you and he will never lead you astray. So God thank you for everything that you do and continue to do. I love you endlessly 🤍♾️ All the praise goes to you 🙌🏽

1 year with you and I am still falling for you more and more each and every day that passes 🤍 Ricky Allen Nunn, I never thought you and I would be together, but they say the best things happen when you least expect them and you truly are the biggest blessing to me. You were there for me when I was at a low point and you were there to pick me up and brush me off when I was feeling down. You made me smile on the days I didn’t want to and you were there to make me laugh when I needed it. I absolutely adore you and think the world of you, and thank you for not only being the most amazing boyfriend but, my best friend , my shoulder to cry on, my ride or die and my partner in crime. You have the kindest heart and sweetest soul. We have gotten so close and you truly have made me a better version of myself and you push me to be the best person I can be each day. You motivate me to be better and you look at things with such a positive, beautiful perspective. I can’t wait to see what the future holds for us 🤍 I am so grateful that God brought you into my life when he did and all I can say is I can’t wait to make more memories with you and cherish every moment we have together. I love you with all my heart! happy 1 year babe 🫶🏽✨😌

The filming of this commercial was epic. Huge shout out to the whole rebel team who helped in making this awesome commercial. Is it over the top??? You better believe it is, because @rebelathleticcheer is over the top, in EVERYTHING, which also now includes this amazing new shoe that I helped to create through my feedback to the Rebel team. I asked and they DELIVERED. This shoe is by far the best I have ever worn in 17 years of cheering. It is a combination of everything that is amazing about Rebel Ruthless, and adds that extra sauce that makes it perfect. It truly is beyond. They feel amazing, super stable, and yet like your tumbling barefoot. I absolutely love them. And for stunting, forget about it. Your bases will thank you. It adds that extra feeling of support and is just right for the bases to hit perfect grips. I'm saying all this because I absolutely believe this shoe will be the best cheer shoe your athlete has ever worn. I don't stand behind brands I don't believe in, but the Rebel brand will forever lead the way when it comes to truly caring about the mechanics of making an amazing shoe.
